data.description: Beautiful updated home in Fountain Valley.  As you enter your new home you are greeted by the large living room and around the corner a separate dining room that leads to the kitchen complete with plenty of cabinets, granite counter tops and new stainless steel appliances.  The family room is off the kitchen with a fireplace, powder room and walk out to the back yard.  The main level features wood laminate floors.  Upstairs is complete with a master bedroom and private bath, two additional bedrooms and a full bath.  The basement has a full bath, bedroom and second living area.  The large back yard has a dog run with shed. Close to Military bases.
